'''夏普萊斯不对称氨羟基化反应'''（{{lang-en|Sharpless asymmetric oxyamination/aminohydroxylation}}）是[[烯烃|烯烃]]在[[烃基|烃基]]、[[亚氨基|亚氨基]]、[[锇|锇]]化合物作用下转化为相应的邻[[氨基|氨基]][[醇|醇]]的反應。<ref>[[K._Barry_Sharpless|Sharpless, K. B.]]; Patrick, D. W.; Truesdale, L. K.; Biller, S. A. ''[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]'' '''1975''', ''97'', 2305. ({{DOI|10.1021/ja00841a071}})</ref><ref>Herranz, E.; Biller, S. A.; [[K._Barry_Sharpless|Sharpless, K. B.]] ''[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]'' '''1978''', ''100'', 3596-3598. ({{DOI|10.1021/ja00479a051}})</ref><ref>Herranz, E.; [[K._Barry_Sharpless|Sharpless, K. B.]] ''[[Org._Syn.|Org. Syn.]]'', Coll. Vol. 7, p.375 (1990); Vol. 61, p.85 (1983). ([http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv7p0375 Article] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv7p0375 |date=20121020174449 }})</ref> 

<br />
